Cargo Bay
   This huge airlock is essentially a giant loading dock, where truckloads of
forms arrive from various printing planets throughout the sector and are
immediately distributed throughout the administrative deck. The only exit on
foot is back the way you came. A spacetruck, its hatch closed, waits in the
cargo bay.

